00:06:05.866 --> 00:06:09.516
tissues. As I mentioned, we started in cartilage repair for a tissue

105
00:06:09.536 --> 00:06:13.196
engineering application, but we recognized even if we had a

106
00:06:13.236 --> 00:06:16.096
perfect therapy to rebuild tissues, if there was inflammation,

107
00:06:16.956 --> 00:06:20.256
