108
00:06:21.096 --> 00:06:22.696
The tissue engineering wouldn't work.

109
00:06:22.736 --> 00:06:24.436
At the same time, collaborators

110
00:06:25.376 --> 00:06:29.196
Nat David had recognized that senescent cells could be an interesting

111
00:06:29.356 --> 00:06:31.336
