112
00:06:32.196 --> 00:06:35.876
for a number of applications, in particular osteoarthritis, where

113
00:06:35.916 --> 00:06:39.876
senescent cells had been seen in cartilage explants being taken

114
00:06:40.136 --> 00:06:42.976
