132
00:07:39.976 --> 00:07:40.616
cell cycle

133
00:07:42.116 --> 00:07:45.456
related gene, was seen to be upregulated in some cells,

134
00:07:45.636 --> 00:07:48.556
although well recognized to be an imperfect marker.

135
00:07:49.536 --> 00:07:52.616
But many of the tools are built around p16.

136
00:07:53.096 --> 00:07:56.876
So these cells are in growth arrest, but they are secreting a

137
00:07:56.936 --> 00:07:59.536
senescence-associated secretary phenotype.

138
00:08:00.056 --> 00:08:04.046
This SASP is what is implicated in the function of

139
00:08:04.046 --> 00:08:07.596
