156
00:09:03.916 --> 00:09:04.876
It's a chronic wound.

157
00:09:05.856 --> 00:09:08.856
Senescent cells, as I mentioned, were recognized to be a part of

158
00:09:09.796 --> 00:09:13.616
the arthritis process. And when we did

159
00:09:13.676 --> 00:09:17.656
senolysis or removal of senescent cells, either through molecules

160
00:09:17.836 --> 00:09:21.136
or through transgenic animals, we could

161
00:09:21.196 --> 00:09:24.936
