723
00:42:18.826 --> 00:42:21.616
Because interferon gamma in the microenvironment can bind these

724
00:42:21.646 --> 00:42:25.506
receptors and activate increased MHC-1, which can

725
00:42:25.526 --> 00:42:29.486
