00:43:29.046 --> 00:43:29.626
cancer model.

743
00:43:31.066 --> 00:43:34.526
I also showed similar things when I was a postdoc in Scott Lowe's group in the

744
00:43:34.566 --> 00:43:36.586
setting of RAS-driven pancreas cancer.

