00:43:36.686 --> 00:43:40.226
We found that a combination of palbociclib, a CDK4/6

746
00:43:40.266 --> 00:43:44.206
inhibitor, and trametinib, a MEK inhibitor, could potently inhibit downstream

747
00:43:44.266 --> 00:43:48.166
