748
00:43:49.366 --> 00:43:50.546
Interesting and similar to

749
00:43:51.806 --> 00:43:55.766
Jennifer's talk, we actually found the SAS in pancreas cancer was very angiogenic.

750
00:43:56.266 --> 00:43:59.046
There are lots of VEGFs, PDGFs secreted.

751
00:43:59.466 --> 00:44:03.386
This lead not only to increased vasculature, but better endothelial activation

752
00:44:03.446 --> 00:44:07.326
marked by P-selectin, VCAM, increased MHC II, that

753
00:44:07.386 --> 00:44:09.966
led to the increased infiltration of CD8 T cells.

754
00:44:10.926 --> 00:44:12.586
However, those T cells weren't really active.

755
00:44:12.666 --> 00:44:16.506
They upregulated PD-1 and the senescent cells themselves, though

