999
00:58:37.178 --> 00:58:37.498
things.

1000
00:58:38.518 --> 00:58:40.958
The resident makeup of the tumor microenvironment,

1001
00:58:42.018 --> 00:58:45.678
the chromatin landscape of the tumor cells, particularly these marks that

1002
00:58:45.758 --> 00:58:47.098
regulate enhancer remodeling,

1003
00:58:48.158 --> 00:58:51.318
and the SASP transcriptional programs. I mentioned a few of these.

1004
00:58:51.378 --> 00:58:54.518
We looked at pro-angiogenic that induce blood vessel formation,

1005
00:58:54.958 --> 00:58:58.738
pro-lymphocyte that activate NK and T cells, pro-myeloid, and also

1006
00:58:58.778 --> 00:59:01.798
ECM remodeling that could potentially drive metastasis.

