1354
01:18:47.994 --> 01:18:51.834
inside you, we also reduce the collagen cuffs, which

1355
01:18:51.874 --> 01:18:55.714
is interesting because apparently you can eliminate senescent cells, and by

1356
01:18:55.774 --> 01:18:59.654
the endogenous fibrolytic activity of the body, you

1357
01:18:59.854 --> 01:19:03.554
even reduce collagen cuffs. So that's a demonstration of in

1358
01:19:03.594 --> 01:19:05.634
vivo clearance of senescent cells.

1359
01:19:07.354 --> 01:19:11.274
Senlyt is of very limited toxicity, to say the

1360
01:19:11.334 --> 01:19:13.514
least. We don't see differences in body weight.

1361
01:19:13.574 --> 01:19:17.194
We don't see differences across major cardinal

1362
01:19:17.294 --> 01:19:20.134
lab or cell blood cell parameters.

1363
01:19:20.854 --> 01:19:24.834
We can use Senlyt as an augmentative or consolidative

1364
01:19:25.054 --> 01:19:28.954
agent upon chemotherapy. You look here at chemotherapy or

1365
01:19:28.994 --> 01:19:32.744
TIS in a lymphoma model where only

1366
01:19:32.774 --> 01:19:36.334
p53-proficient lymphoma cells with an apoptotic block

1367
01:19:36.394 --> 01:19:40.330
underwent cellular senescence.And if we take those cells, apply

1368
01:19:40.470 --> 01:19:43.650
