1369
01:19:43.690 --> 01:19:47.590
p53-deficient cells. And we can test that in vivo.

1370
01:19:47.630 --> 01:19:51.330
We administer lymphoma cells, lymphomas grow in

1371
01:19:51.410 --> 01:19:55.330
recipient fully immune competent mice, and then we first

1372
01:19:55.370 --> 01:19:57.980
apply chemotherapy and second senlytic.

1373
01:19:57.980 --> 01:20:00.970
And it's senlytic which in senescent lymphomas,

1374
01:20:01.810 --> 01:20:05.450
extends survival of the mice in virtually all settings.

1375
01:20:05.530 --> 01:20:09.230
But if we use p53 null lymphomas, the addition of a second

