1385
01:20:42.729 --> 01:20:46.570
You see that in the middle. And if we provide senlytic, we can

1386
01:20:46.610 --> 01:20:49.170
reduce these p16-positive lesions.

1387
01:20:49.190 --> 01:20:52.910
That is particularly nice to look at the ears of these mice, you see these

1388
01:20:53.510 --> 01:20:56.730
dark spots in the ear, and if you provide senlytic, they

1389
01:20:57.130 --> 01:21:00.690
