1390
01:21:00.810 --> 01:21:04.750
clearance of senescent cells. We can drive this a step further,

1391
01:21:04.760 --> 01:21:06.730
and that's a pretty interesting model.

1392
01:21:07.250 --> 01:21:10.170
Based on tamoxifen, we can turn on BRAF.

1393
01:21:10.250 --> 01:21:13.770
But we can use tamoxifen in addition in this compound mouse

1394
01:21:14.450 --> 01:21:17.850
containing two p53 ER alleles

1395
01:21:18.590 --> 01:21:22.270
to restore functional wild-type

1396
01:21:22.370 --> 01:21:26.350
similar p53 levels. In this setting, we get the same result as

1397
01:21:26.390 --> 01:21:29.730
you just saw, but we have the opportunity to remove

1398
01:21:29.810 --> 01:21:33.090
tamoxifen at some point in time, which means that there are

1399
01:21:33.130 --> 01:21:36.690
BRAF-positive lesions now no longer with active

