01:21:36.730 --> 01:21:40.350
p53, therefore on their way to form melanomas.

1401
01:21:40.380 --> 01:21:42.190
And that's indeed what's happening in this model.

1402
01:21:42.230 --> 01:21:44.470
You see the lesion at the back of the mouse.

1403
01:21:44.530 --> 01:21:48.510
You see the skin tumor, and you can even see metastasis to inguinal

1404
01:21:48.529 --> 01:21:51.870
lymph nodes in the lung. But if we now in this window of

1405
01:21:51.950 --> 01:21:55.790
opportunity where we have only OIS nevus lesions

1406
01:21:55.810 --> 01:21:58.910
