1407
01:21:58.990 --> 01:22:02.740
We see delayed and reduced melanoma genesis in

1408
01:22:02.790 --> 01:22:04.590
this model due to senlytic.

1409
01:22:06.110 --> 01:22:09.330
We can also target RAS senescent cells.

1410
01:22:09.450 --> 01:22:13.350
This is simply retroviral provision of oncogenic

1411
01:22:13.390 --> 01:22:17.290
RAS. And you see on the left, we can provide senlytic and eliminate

