1414
01:22:24.530 --> 01:22:27.950
The interesting point is now using an old-fashioned

1415
01:22:28.330 --> 01:22:32.150
chemical cancerogene, NMU, N-methyl-N-nitrosourea,

1416
01:22:32.450 --> 01:22:36.110
